    "DiskCleaner": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "DiskCleaner"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "DiskCleaner 每次把文件移到废纸篓时，都会记录在这里。": {},
    "DiskCleaner 现在可以扫描磁盘上的文件了。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "DiskCleaner can now scan files on your disk."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "DiskCleaner 需要完全磁盘访问，才能扫描系统各处的缓存、日志和大文件。这项权限只能由你在系统设置中手动授予。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "DiskCleaner needs Full Disk Access to scan caches, logs, and large files across the system. This permission can only be granted manually in System Settings."
          }
        }
      }
    },
